    {
      "id": "c10691f9-af08-426d-8414-75677105a7cf",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Learning analytics is being constantly integrated in learning environments. However, most of the markers for student success derive from self-reported measures. Study compares the effectiveness of logs vs self-reports as effective representations of achievement goals. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "c10691f9-af08-426d-8414-75677105a7cf",
